<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="12Dec1933"><font color="red">12 December 1933</font> <i>NLRH</i> (from Bennett Cerf to Paul L&eacute;on): Have you made final arrangements as yet for the publication of WORK IN PROGRESS in America? We should dearly like to publish this book and bring it out, possibly in the format that will duplicate that of ULYSSES. </div>
